________________________________________
Short Summary
SCC in OpenShift:
•	controls container security permissions
•	protects host system
•	restricts privileged operations
Steps to allow special permissions:
1️⃣ Create service account
oc create serviceaccount sa-name
2️⃣ Assign SCC
oc adm policy add-scc-to-user anyuid -z sa-name
3️⃣ Attach service account to deployment
oc set serviceaccount deployment/app sa-name

